<h1>Welcome to the Secret Number Game!</h1>

<p>To play, just pick a number. If you guess the secret number, you win.</p>

<br/>

<h2>Pick a number:</h2>

<% (1..5).each do |number| %>
<%= link_to image_tag("secret_numbers/#{number}.jpeg"), secret_number_path(number) %>

<% end %>

